Movie Recommendation System

How to run the programs:

cosine_similarity.py will run simply by using the command:

    >> python cosine_similarity.py

This will output all 3 files: result5.txt, result10.txt, and result20.txt

pearson.py which includes the modifications IUF and Case Amplification
will run per test file provided as an argument via the command line i.e.

    >> python pearson.py test5.txt
    >> python pearson.py test10.txt
    >> python pearson.py test20.txt

item_based.py which is implemented using adjusted cosine similarity
will run per test file provided as an argument via the command line i.e.

    >> python item_based.py test5.txt
    >> python item_based.py test10.txt
    >> python item_based.py test20.txt

combine.py (self made algorithm) will run given the non rounded files
provided in the directories: /pearson_outputs and /cosine_outputs
This program will run simply with the command:

    >> python combine.py
